annel": 0, "num_words": 59, "start": 82.490005, "end": 109.035}, {"sentences": [{"text": "Mhmm.", "start": 109.17, "end": 109.49}], "channel": 1, "num_words": 1, "start": 109.17, "end": 109.49}, {"sentences": [{"text": "behavior behavior in which 118 university students were split into three groups to take part in Stroop takes tasks tasks tasks.", "start": 111.33, "end": 123.409996}, {"text": "During Stroop tasks, participations are shown the word for a color, but the font will be in a different color.", "start": 124.455, "end": 133.015}, {"text": "For example, they will see the word green but written in red letters.", "start": 133.015, "end": 137.41501}], "channel": 0, "num_words": 54, "start": 111.33, "end": 137.41501}, {"sentences": [{"text": "Re written.", "start": 137.47, "end": 138.43}, {"text": "Written.", "start": 138.43, "end": 138.83}], "channel": 1, "num_words": 3, "start": 137.47, "end": 138.83}, {"sentences": [{"text": "But written but written in red letters but written in red letters.", "start": 139.55, "end": 145.47}, {"text": "Participate participants have to name the color of the letters while ignoring the word they spell, which takes mental effort and becomes more difficult if they lose", "start": 145.47, "end": 157.375}], "channel": 0, "num_words": 39, "start": 139.55, "end": 157.375}, {"sentences": [{"text": "Because.", "start": 157.135, "end": 157.775}], "channel": 1, "num_words": 1, "start": 157.135, "end": 157.775}, {"sentences": [{"text": "focus.", "start": 157.375, "end": 158.09502}, {"text": "Becomes becomes and becomes more difficult if they lose focus.", "start": 158.815, "end": 162.65501}, {"text": "For the for this experiment for this experiment, the researchers set up these true tasks, on a computer with an interface that, looked like an iPhone.", "start": 163.615, "end": 176.27}, {"text": "As they did the tasks, participate participants would occasionally see notifications from", "start": 176.75, "end": 183.205}], "channel": 0, "num_words": 49, "start": 157.375, "end": 183.205}, {"sentences": [{"text": "Occasionally.", "start": 182.935, "end": 183.895}], "channel": 1, "num_words": 1, "start": 182.935, "end": 183.895}, {"sentences": [{"text": "their", "start": 183.205, "end": 183.445}], "channel": 0, "num_words": 1, "start": 183.205, "end": 183.445}, {"sentences": [{"text": "Occasionally.", "start": 183.97499, "end": 184.69499}, {"text": "Mhmm.", "start": 184.69499, "end": 185.095}], "channel": 1, "num_words": 2, "start": 183.97499, "end": 185.095}, {"sentences": [{"text": "occasionally occasionally.", "start": 184.80501, "end": 186.245}, {"text": "They would occasionally see notifications from their most used phones phone apps appear on their computer screen.", "start": 186.245, "end": 194.16501}], "channel": 0, "num_words": 19, "start": 184.80501, "end": 194.16501}, {"sentences": [{"text": "Mhmm.", "start": 194.37, "end": 194.85}], "channel": 1, "num_words": 1, "start": 194.37, "end": 194.85}, {"sentences": [{"text": "One group was told that their smartphones were actually signed signed signed the", "start": 195.15001, "end": 204.11}], "channel": 0, "num_words": 13, "start": 195.15001, "end": 204.11}, {"sentences": [{"text": "Yep.", "start": 203.855, "end": 204.33499}], "channel": 1, "num_words": 1, "start": 203.855, "end": 204.33499}, {"sentences": [{"text": "computer.", "start": 204.11, "end": 204.91}], "channel": 0, "num_words": 1, "start": 204.11, "end": 204.91}, {"sentences": [{"text": "I", "start": 204.33499, "end": 204.575}], "channel": 1, "num_words": 1, "start": 204.33499, "end": 204.575}, {"sentences": [{"text": "How?", "start": 206.83, "end": 207.47002}, {"text": "Is it?", "start": 208.03, "end": 208.43001}], "channel": 0, "num_words": 3, "start": 206.83, "end": 208.43001}, {"sentences": [{"text": "synced model,", "start": 209.61499, "end": 210.815}], "channel": 1, "num_words": 2, "start": 209.61499, "end": 210.815}, {"sentences": [{"text": "Synced.", "start": 210.71501, "end": 211.515}], "channel": 0, "num_words": 1, "start": 210.71501, "end": 211.515}, {"sentences": [{"text": "maybe.", "start": 210.815, "end": 211.055}], "channel": 1, "num_words": 1, "start": 210.815, "end": 211.055}, {"sentences": [{"text": "Synced.", "start": 211.515, "end": 211.91501}, {"text": "Okay.", "start": 211.91501, "end": 212.47502}, {"text": "Synced to the computer.", "start": 212.55501, "end": 214.07501}, {"text": "One group was told that their smartphones were actually synced to the computer.", "start": 214.07501, "end": 218.55501}, {"text": "So they believed that the notifications they got on the computer were real and personal.", "start": 218.55501, "end": 223.43501}], "channel": 0, "num_words": 34, "start": 211.515, "end": 223.43501}, {"sentences": [{"text": "The next group was told that any notification they saw were for someone else.", "start": 223.90001, "end": 228.78001}], "channel": 0, "num_words": 14, "start": 223.90001, "end": 228.78001}, {"sentences": [{"text": "Mhmm.", "start": 228.73, "end": 229.21}], "channel": 1, "num_words": 1, "start": 228.73, "end": 229.21}, {"sentences": [{"text": "And the last group''s notifications were blurred, so they would see a pop out pop up, but couldn''t read any information.", "start": 228.94, "end": 236.62001}, {"text": "The researchers found that just one notification of any type could slow down a participant''s cognitive processing for around seven seconds, slowing the action time on the stroke tasks.", "start": 237.35501, "end": 249.675}, {"text": "But the effect was particularly strong among those who fought fought.", "start": 250.85, "end": 257.97}, {"text": "They were they were", "start": 257.97, "end": 260.37}], "channel": 0, "num_words": 65, "start": 228.94, "end": 260.37}, {"sentences": [{"text": "Sorry.", "start": 260.195, "end": 260.755}], "channel": 1, "num_words": 1, "start": 260.195, "end": 260.755}, {"sentences": [{"text": "seeing", "start": 260.37, "end": 260.61002}], "channel": 0, "num_words": 1, "start": 260.37, "end": 260.61002}, {"sentences": [{"text": "Sorry.", "start": 260.755, "end": 261.155}, {"text": "Thought.", "start": 261.155, "end": 261.635}], "channel": 1, "num_words": 2, "start": 260.755, "end": 261.635}, {"sentences": [{"text": "fought fought.", "start": 262.21, "end": 263.25}, {"text": "Who those who fought, they were seeing notifications from their own phone.", "start": 263.805, "end": 269.08502}, {"text": "And the more they wanted to check a notification and the stronger the emotional response, the more, the more, their reaction time was delayed.", "start": 269.325, "end": 278.125}, {"text": "Seven", "start": 278.58, "end": 278.98}], "channel": 0, "num_words": 39, "start": 262.21, "end": 278.98}, {"sentences": [{"text": "Mhmm.", "start": 278.6, "end": 279.08002}], "channel": 1, "num_words": 1, "start": 278.6, "end": 279.08002}, {"sentences": [{"text": "sec might not seem like a lot.", "start": 278.98, "end": 281.62}, {"text": "However, Hippologt Fournier, one of the study authors told CPOST, Even short disruption when repeated dose dozens or hundreds of time per day may meaningfully affect concentration and", "start": 281.62, "end": 301.305}], "channel": 0, "num_words": 35, "start": 278.98, "end": 301.305}]}}}'::jsonb);
