 looking forward to it. I I used to I used to scroll my phone. So, like, searching notifications sometimes. So I it''s it has shown me that I still need to improve. But as I told you, this situation helped me a lot that I turn off my notifications. It''s one step to to achieve my goal, let''s say, if it is a goal. Yeah? When I started to to get off my notifications, I felt this this sensation this sensation of of of losing something. But I but now I consider that if something is really important something is really important, someone will will get to me. Yeah? But we''ll contact yeah. But but when what we nowadays, we have a lot of notifications about", "confidence": 0.9941406, "words": [{"word": "yeah", "start": 0, "end": 0.88, "confidence": 0.66625977, "punctuated_word": "Yeah."}, {"word": "mhmm", "start": 2.56, "end": 3.04, "confidence": 0.7949219, "punctuated_word": "Mhmm."}, {"word": "activity", "start": 5.68, "end": 6.08, "confidence": 0.7125244, "punctuated_word": "Activity."}, {"word": "good", "start": 6.08, "end": 6.3199997, "confidence": 0.5732422, "punctuated_word": "Good"}, {"word": "activity", "start": 6.3199997, "end": 6.64, "confidence": 0.9667969, "punctuated_word": "activity."}, {"word": "i", "start": 23.634998, "end": 23.875, "confidence": 0.93359375, "punctuated_word": "I"}, {"word": "i", "start": 23.875, "end": 24.275, "confidence": 0.49267578, "punctuated_word": "I"}, {"word": "thought", "start": 24.275, "end": 24.595, "confidence": 0.97265625, "punctuated_word": "thought"}, {"word": "that", "start": 24.595, "end": 24.835, "confidence": 0.9970703, "punctuated_word": "that"}, {"word": "it", "start": 24.835, "end": 25.235, "confidence": 0.93408203, "punctuated_word": "it"}, {"word": "would", "start": 25.235, "end": 25.395, "confidence": 0.9633789, "punctuated_word": "would"}, {"word": "be", "start": 25.395, "end": 25.555, "confidence": 0.99316406, "punctuated_word": "be"}, {"word": "great", "start": 25.555, "end": 25.715, "confidence": 0.7285156, 